cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.DB. 

The paper deals with knowledge graph completion, which is a task in artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves natural language processing (cs.CL) as it uses text descriptions to learn semantic features. The use of Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also deals with information retrieval (cs.IR) as it aims to expand the coverage of knowledge graphs. Finally, knowledge graph completion is a subfield of databases (cs.DB).
